label: Malaria treatment
codebookDescription: If the participant is RDT positive and male, he should be offered treatment with Coartem. If the participant is RDT positive and female and not pregnant, she should be offered treatment with Coartem. If the participant is pregnant she should be offered quinine and/or clindamycin
